INTRUDER!

DarkMouse::

monitor showed a Pred at the entrance of the base.  She looked at 
Twister, "Grab your weapon and follow me." She had her gun in hand 
and ran to the intruder.  She saw Dracona nearing the entrance.  She 
raised her gun and aimed at the intruder.
"HALT! IDENTIFY YOURSELF! NO FALSE MOVES OR THE AUTOGUNS BLOW YOU TO 
SCRAP!"
